 Shygirl 与 Isabella Lovestory 和 PinkPantheress 合作推出新单曲《True Religion》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-teams-up-with-isabella-lovestory-and-pinkpantheress-on-new-single-true-religion-3831489?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=害羞女孩与伊莎贝拉爱情故事和粉红豹在新单一真实宗教上合作Anagricel DuranThu, 23 Jan 2025 16:06:51 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3831489 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="害羞女孩和粉红豹。图片来源：曼尼·卡拉贝尔和吉尔伯特·弗洛雷斯，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是她即将推出的 EP“Club Shy Room 2”中发行的第三首单曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-teams-up-with-isabella-lovestory-and-pinkpantheress-on-new-single-true-religion-3831489">Shygirl 与 Isabella Lovestory 和 PinkPantheress 合作的新单曲“True Religion”</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="害羞女孩和粉红豹。图片来源：曼尼·卡拉贝尔和吉尔伯特·弗洛雷斯，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-and-Pinkpantheress.-Credit-Manny-Carabel-and-Gilbert-Flores-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Shygirl">Shygirl</a>与 Isabella Lovestory 和<a href="/artists/PinkPantheress">PinkPantheress</a>联手制作了她的最新单曲“True Religion”。看看下面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/shygirl-london-debut-album-review-nymph-radar-3319411#:~:text=Its%20a%20brilliantly%20saucy%20highlight,wholly%20unique%20in%20its%20execution.">Shygirl – “Nymph”评论：流行规则破坏者在朋友的帮助下大放异彩</a></strong></li></ul><p>在这首歌曲中，三位歌手齐聚一堂，创作了一首时尚而迷人的舞池赞歌。 <em>“你知道你爱我就像一个网络摄像头女孩/网络摄像头，网络摄像头，网络摄像头女孩，”</em> Shygirl 用充满加勒比海风格的脉动节奏唱道。</p><p>出生于洪都拉斯的伊莎贝拉爱情故事用她的母语西班牙语提供了一段激动人心的诗句，而粉红豹则用她空灵柔和的声音唱着第三节诗： <em>“真正的宗教，没有更高/真正的宗教，你激励。”</em></p><p> 《True Religion》是 Shygirl 即将于 2 月 28 日发行的 EP《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-announces-new-ep-club-shy-room-2-shares-single-fme-3820685">Club Shy Room 2</a> 》中发行的第三首单曲。这首歌是继之前发行的由 Yseult 和 Saweetie 合作的《F*Me》和《Immaculate》之后发行的。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Shygirl - True Religion ft. Isabella Lovestory 和 PinkPantheress（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JAaqo2wonMk?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《Club Shy Room 2》由 Mura Masa 和 Oscar Scheller 共同制作，Nick León 和 Blue May 客串出演。 Jorja Smith、BAMBII 和 SadBoi 等人也作为曲目出现在 EP 中。</p><p> Shygirl 在社交媒体上宣布推出《Club Shy Room 2》EP 时表示，该系列将“只是让派对继续下去的一点小东西”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3831507" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3831507" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3831507" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Shygirl &#39;Club Shy Room 2&#39; EP 艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Shygirl-Club-Shy-Room-2-EP-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3831507" class="wp-caption-text"> Shygirl &#39;Club Shy Room 2&#39; EP 艺术作品。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>Shygirl 的“Club Shy Room 2”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1.《我的心》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“Flex（壮举。BAMBII）”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“完美（壮举。Saweetie）”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“F*Me（壮举。Yseult）”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“Wifey Riddim（壮举。Jorja Smith 和 SadBoi）”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“真正的宗教（壮举。伊莎贝拉爱情故事和粉红豹）”</strong></p><p> Shygirl 于 2022 年发行了她的首张录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/shygirl-london-debut-album-review-nymph-radar-3319411#:~:text=Its%20a%20brilliantly%20saucy%20highlight,wholly%20unique%20in%20its%20execution.">《Nymph》</a> 。在四星评论中， <em>NME</em>称赞这位艺术家创造了“闪闪发光的俱乐部声音拼贴画，每个元素在执行上都是独一无二的”。</p><p>它补充道：“在她为期待已久的首张专辑付出了数年的努力之后，这张唱片显然是值得的：这张唱片惊人地提醒人们为什么 Shygirl 是首都最聪明的人才之一。”</p><p>此后，她分享了 EP <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-announces-new-ep-club-shy-releases-single-tell-me-featuring-boys-noize-listen-3572824">“Club Shy”</a>及其姊妹项目“Club Shy RMX”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-announces-2024-uk-arena-tour-with-shygirl-3612882">Shygirl 最近支持 Charli XCX 进行“Brat”英国竞技场巡演</a>，巡演地点包括曼彻斯特、伦敦、伯明翰和格拉斯哥。她还与 Charli 合作，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">她的“Brat”混音专辑</a>中重新制作了“365”。 <em>《NME》</em>称赞这次合作是“两分钟纯粹、纯粹的享乐主义”。</p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad2 id_ad_content-horiz-center">其他消息方面， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/confidence-man-shygirl-and-more-to-join-barry-cant-swim-at-all-points-east-2025-3811109">Shygirl 将于今年夏天在伦敦举办的 All Points East 头条秀中为 Barry Can&#39;t Swim 开场</a>。她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/confidence-man">Confidence Man</a>和 DJ Heartstring 等歌手一起出现在阵容中。</div><p></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/shygirl-teams-up-with-isabella-lovestory-and-pinkpantheress-on-new-single-true-religion-3831489">Shygirl 与 Isabella Lovestory 和 PinkPantheress 合作的新单曲“True Religion”</a>首先在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上发布。</p> ;
